<paragraph id="59658F14FD33B6941AC5BC54B8425FBF" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<bibRefCitation id="131A0E7ED4338C47989AF13FBB0E9869" author="Stark, BP" journalOrPublisher="Illiesia" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="19 - 54" refId="B52" refString="Stark, BP, Sivec, I, 2008. New species and records of Neoperla (Plecoptera: Perlidae) from Vietnam. Illiesia 4 (3): 19 - 54" title="New species and records of Neoperla (Plecoptera: Perlidae) from Vietnam." volume="4" year="2008">Stark and Sivec (2008)</bibRefCitation>
originally described this species from Vietnam, and 
<bibRefCitation id="507D023C9F885329290CF8BE53BFD7C6" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4790.3.6" author="Mo, RR" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="515 - 524" refId="B42" refString="Mo, RR, Wang, GQ, Li, WH, 2020a. A new species and two new records of the Neoperla diehli subgroup of the N. montivaga group (Plecoptera: Perlidae) from China. Zootaxa 4790 (3): 515 - 524, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4790.3.6" title="A new species and two new records of the Neoperla diehli subgroup of the N. montivaga group (Plecoptera: Perlidae) from China." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4790.3.6" volume="4790" year="2020 a">Mo et al. (2020a)</bibRefCitation>
described a new record in Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region. The terminalia and aedeagus of our specimen fit the original description of 
<bibRefCitation id="A9D58025FB550C8A9FC7ACFEE0A825A4" author="Stark, BP" journalOrPublisher="Illiesia" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="19 - 54" refId="B52" refString="Stark, BP, Sivec, I, 2008. New species and records of Neoperla (Plecoptera: Perlidae) from Vietnam. Illiesia 4 (3): 19 - 54" title="New species and records of Neoperla (Plecoptera: Perlidae) from Vietnam." volume="4" year="2008">Stark and Sivec (2008)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="80386E06B6157F6132D5DDD929101B59" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="﻿concluding remarks">
<paragraph id="2C05C39F6CC21E47D941814CFFE0129B" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Concluding remarks</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A3D688F89CDF0C6B1E59A0C8E00158D7" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<taxonomicName id="B064EDFD595807496EEA9F94E7F8AD21" authorityName="Needham" authorityYear="1905" class="Insecta" family="Perlidae" genus="Neoperla" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Neoperla" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="02876A2492B64B0F41E4FDAFC34146A0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Neoperla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was divided into the 
<taxonomicName id="B44A3A0F0C2C5A523683BF76D50CC432" baseAuthorityName="Newman" baseAuthorityYear="1839" class="Insecta" family="Perlidae" genus="Neoperla" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Neoperla clymene" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="clymene">
<emphasis id="01C30D9A60BAAA96E8A1480CAD3F71B5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Neoperla clymene</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group and the 
<taxonomicName id="A7A68EEDB80BDEAE41A901CCB0E973C1" class="Insecta" family="Perlidae" genus="Neoperla" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Neoperla montivaga" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="montivaga">
<emphasis id="7AD5C6F93EDBC413FEF5701578BE217C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Neoperla montivaga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group by 
<bibRefCitation id="E6402CCCB139DD8C3A15612A6C91ADBD" author="Zwick, P" journalOrPublisher="Spixiana" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="167 - 204" refId="B75" refString="Zwick, P, 1983. The Neoperla of Sumatra and Java (Indonesia) (Plecoptera: Perlidae). Spixiana 6: 167 - 204" title="The Neoperla of Sumatra and Java (Indonesia) (Plecoptera: Perlidae)." volume="6" year="1983">Zwick (1983)</bibRefCitation>
. The 
<taxonomicName id="3BE0BF18530DFD1C5EC106B6B615E3D2" class="Insecta" genus="N." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="N. clymene" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="clymene">
<emphasis id="D9B6F19DA7FC44082FE68EA080C8C67A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">N. clymene</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group currently includes more than 150 species, and the 
<taxonomicName id="F06017CB45E258D68A3A587385663EAD" class="Insecta" genus="N." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="N. montivaga" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="montivaga">
<emphasis id="8B267146B7835C91BAF39BE7C4CF522E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">N. montivaga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group includes over 123 species worldwide (
<bibRefCitation id="742A60C7A18C888AC34CAE35F7877339" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5004.2.3" author="Huo, QB" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="288 - 310" refId="B20" refString="Huo, QB, Du, YZ, Zhu, BQ, Yu, L, 2021. Notes on Neoperla sinensis Chu, 1928 and Neoperla anjiensis Yang Yang, 1998, with descriptions of new species of Neoperla from China (Plecoptera: Perlidae). Zootaxa 5004 (2): 288 - 310, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5004.2.3" title="Notes on Neoperla sinensis Chu, 1928 and Neoperla anjiensis Yang Yang, 1998, with descriptions of new species of Neoperla from China (Plecoptera: Perlidae)." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5004.2.3" volume="5004" year="2021">Huo et al. 2021</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="208CEBD761CC2CD2EDAF7ED5D27FA6EF" DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1056.61565" author="Mo, RR" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="191 - 206" refId="B44" refString="Mo, RR, Wang, GQ, Li, WH, Muranyi, D, 2021a. Two new species and one new record of Neoperla (Plecoptera, Perlidae) from Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region, China. ZooKeys 1056: 191 - 206, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1056.61565" title="Two new species and one new record of Neoperla (Plecoptera, Perlidae) from Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region, China." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1056.61565" volume="1056" year="2021 a">Mo et al. 2021a</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B57E2285D48DEBBBDF9E3E4A54F990AE" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
So far 11 species of 
<taxonomicName id="7D78B52FA2F5E7005EC82C478F07875E" genus="Neoeprla" lsidName="Neoeprla" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="7908968420D4C80F827CECFE6BC88005" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Neoeprla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have been recorded from Yunnan Province, including the two new species and one species newly recorded in this paper. Among the six endemic species of 
<taxonomicName id="EF8FA0D2FA604C09E86136B2FF7BBBF7" authorityName="Needham" authorityYear="1905" class="Insecta" family="Perlidae" genus="Neoperla" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Neoperla" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="390EF644BD99E0239F52313C5054E69C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Neoperla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, including the two new species listed below- 
<taxonomicName id="EB61E5E0E9FEA4B39797D30A8F2792C6" class="Insecta" genus="N." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="N. lihuae" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lihuae">
<emphasis id="ACBA0F41D4150B73F626173120C28A99" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">N. lihuae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="D78984950EE0E8E3B05E9A0E62CE4728" class="Insecta" genus="N." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="N. yanlii" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yanlii">
<emphasis id="15CA860893D7DA98F729862A52AB9B89" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">N. yanlii</emphasis>
